                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "Resolved on Feb 27, 2026 at 3:30 PM. The storage latency issue was caused by a misconfigured cache eviction policy during a routine deployment. The configuration was reverted and caching performance returned to normal within 15 minutes of the fix being applied.",
